steps.name: Given I am login on staging env by created timestamp project
Debug step:
When I navigate to menu "Database" with submenu "Database Editor"
Then I should see Database screen display
When I add new table with Name "jit015e" and Comment "[INDEX-TEXT]"
Then I should see the table with Name "jit015e" display
When I add new column with Name "indextext" Type "text" for Table name "jit015e"
When I open popup to see column infos Name "indextext" of table with Name "jit015e"
When I check checkbox popup Name "Indexed"
When I sleep 1
When I press Save button modal popup
Then I should see dropdown Index column index "1" of Index number "1" of table "jit015e" has value "indextext" in retry mode
